Real Madrid face Atletico Madrid at the Bernabeu on Sunday . 
  Carlo Ancelotti and Diego Simeone were runners-up at the Ballon d'Or in January . 
  The Italian reportedly said life in Madrid would be easier if Atletico weren't around . 
  Atletico visit Real in the Champions League semi-final second leg . 
  Real have struggled against Atletico in recent years and lost 4-0 in the La Liga derby in February . 
  Real need to win the game to progress in the competition . 
 